   - Present the result as a single numerical value, representing the money left at the end of the scenario.

8. **Final Answer Format:**
   - On the last line, write only: '#### <number>', where <number> is the integer or decimal value of the answer, as appropriate.
   - Do NOT include units, explanatory text, or additional formatting after that line.

