5. **Show all intermediate calculations** as you go, labeling each step for clarity.

6. **Final answer formatting:** On the last line of your solution, write the answer as '#### <number>', where <number> is the numeric value of the answer (no extra text or explanation). Use an integer if the answer is whole, or the decimal/fraction if it is not.

Your response should not include any commentary outside of the logical, stepwise process and should only end with the specified answer format.
