   - If fencing a square, always compute full perimeter as 4 × side length, not area or other figure.
   - Ensure distinction between area (square units) and perimeter (linear units).
   - For ‘feet will not be fenced,’ final calculation must be (Total Perimeter) - (Perimeter Purchasable with budget).

